title: Special Development Zone (SDZ):-Special Development Zone (SDZ) is a zone which is to be developed predominantly for society at large with emphasis on AffordableHousing, POS and necessary Social infrastructures
clause_text: Special Development Zone (SDZ):-Special Development Zone (SDZ) is a zone which is to be developed predominantly for society at large with emphasis on AffordableHousing, POS and necessary Social infrastructures. The development of SDZshall be under the provision of regulation 33(8)
